# Real VPN configs — anyone dropping a .conf or .json into the repo
# folder for testing must NOT have it committed. WireGuard configs
# contain a PrivateKey; Xray/v2ray configs contain UUIDs/passwords;
# .ovpn for OpenVPN. All are user-secret and stay out of git.
*.conf
*.ovpn
test_*.json
sample_*.json

# Ad-hoc emulator screenshots saved during manual testing.
build-screen.png
